2011_March 22 
Christopher Nolan directs &#x27;Inception&#x27; with Leonardo DiCaprio starring
as Dom Cobb the man kept away from his kids for reasons no other than
the consequences of his thieving skills, not any thieving skills tho,
psychological thieving skills with dreaming a dream and planting ideas,
he tries all the possible ways of trying to reach them and he gets the
team together and a businessmen who can get him back to his kids with
no problems. All looks simple so far but then while training they
experience the full force of ex-wife Mrs. Cobb who gets caught up in
what is a dream and what is reality. The film won four academy awards
and grossed over $825million at the box office
